Today, exactly 69 years ago, Haim (Victor) Arlozorov was murdered in what is believed to be a political assasination.

The killer was never found.
- So, why don't you have sex? - He doesn't want to. - Who is "he"? - The one I want to... - ... - But there are others - But I don't want to...

"loneliness is not a phase"

- Alice In Chains

"...when they find you on the highway
and you're lying in the rain
and they ask you how you doin'
of course you say you can't complain
when they squeeze for information
thats where you got to play it dumb
you're just saying that you're waiting
for the miracle to come..."
Its the evenings that kill most.
Does anybody know why the laser-eye of the optical mouse keeps blinking excessively even after the PC was shut down?

Papa had a birthday yesterday.
..But then again, I don't have a father, remember?

I would have been so much happier as a White Russian Borzoy...

<font size=-1>...or a Blue Great Dane </font>
